{"tid":1856000,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"本地感染！長康邨75歲男確診","createTime":"2020-02-01T11:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:14:52.000Z","uid":78873,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7afbad02c2c991e8f07b51e5980216f460c568","tid":1856000,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"爆啦爆啦 社區爆發啦終於 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qECiva.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qECiva.gif&h=bc14d1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母林鄭唔撚封關 而家隨時萬國封鎖香港自己困獸鬥  呢鋪真係10000蚊儲糧都玩唔撚起 到時全民染病 點撚樣醫? 幾十萬病人一齊殺上去搵林鄭不是夢<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港至今有十三宗新型冠狀病毒的確診個案，其中三人情況嚴重。衞生防護中心指，其中居於青衣長康邨75歲確診的老翁，不排除屬本地感染個案，仍正追蹤其染病源頭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378890&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378890%26home%3D1&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=e4e28f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378890%26home%3D1&h=e86390c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378890&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"dc10e6959c090aa007a5afe06fae904939c7658d","tid":1856000,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"住美景<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd49af657ad47c30b2bf69ad47670c92f671c10a","tid":1856000,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88593aa7130e7adda0d05489410d23428d6912c0","tid":1856000,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"爆啦爆啦"},{"pid":"b8661a879b218a921c88233f6925302d392b1a83","tid":1856000,"uid":78873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"青衣先爆 根住到荃灣 一路爆落去九龍新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eead4cb9ebbbcf134662eedc99781892b2f2613","tid":1856000,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467f41de0396c9e77cfb7fb25365f0d9575ba86d","tid":1856000,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】本港至今確診13人感染新型冠狀病毒，3人情況嚴重。衞生防護中心表示，居於青衣長康邨的75歲男確診患者，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自己及家人都沒去過湖北，不排除屬本地感染個案，可能是被社區的隱形病人傳染，情況令人擔心。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n13名在本港確診的病人中，大部分在潛伏期去過武漢或者被家人傳染，唯獨居於青衣長康邨的75歲男患者，病發前15天從順德返港，之後去過五次澳門，病發前八天都留在香港。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心分析，患者可能屬本地感染個案，<span style=\"color: red;\">病毒有機會已在本港社區蔓延。</span><br />\n<br />\n衞生署表示，由於未找到病人受感染途徑，難以修改懷疑個案呈報準則，而醫管局會為所有肺炎病人進行快速測試，以減低潛在病人在普通病房傳播的風險。<br />\n<br />\n這名病人曾在瑪嘉烈醫院普通病房留醫七天才隔離，與他同房的九名病人是密切接觸者，目前在醫院或度假營隔離。與他接觸過的70多名醫護有戴口罩和手套，僅需接受醫學監測。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署亦指，有兩名病人相信是被妻子或父母傳染，認為病毒在密切接觸者之間傳染性高，不止是有限度人傳人。<br />\n<br />\n目前確診病人中，有三人情況嚴重，兩人在深切治療部需要聞氧氣，另一人出現氣促。"},{"pid":"6400fd35b688760a6235dabf250b24c5e3ecbbde","tid":1856000,"uid":120955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"藍區青衣廢老第一爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c56af07fd85e54499cfaa0b4d51de5a31c7d1a7","tid":1856000,"uid":265980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b7afbad02c2c991e8f07b51e5980216f460c568","tid":1856000,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"爆啦爆啦 社區爆發啦終於 <br />\n<img src=\"https://